
=Description=

"A "resource pool" is a network of persons, who use something together, give things to each other for free or share it. That can be the inhabitants of a house but also a network of friends. An important base is confidence. The "resource pool" is a network of people where you can ask for help. These networks are based on the idea of giving for free – not exchanging things."
(http://www.whopools.net/index.php?page=static&pageid=about)


